                        チェックする
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div id="result-area" class="hidden mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100 fade-in">
                    <div id="auto-success-msg" class="hidden mb-6 p-4 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-3 text-green-700 font-bold">
                        <div class="bg-green-500 text-white p-1 rounded-full">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        正解です！
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 text-xs font-bold rounded-lg mb-3">模範解答</span>
                        <p id="correct-answer" class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 break-words leading-relaxed"></p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div id="manual-buttons" class="flex gap-4">
                        <button onclick="recordAndNext(true)" class="flex-1 bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-600 text-white py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold shadow-lg transition-all active:scale-95">○ 正解</button>
                        <button onclick="recordAndNext(false)" class="flex-1 bg-rose-500 hover:bg-rose-600 text-white py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold shadow-lg transition-all active:scale-95">× 不正解</button>
                    </div>

                    <div id="next-button-area" class="hidden">
                        <button onclick="recordAndNext(true)" class="w-full bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold shadow-lg shadow-indigo-200 transition-all active:scale-95 flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
                            次へ進む
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                            </svg>
                        </button>
